name: Fiona Cai

services.title: Front-End Development
services.description: I've made sites for all types of things: student council, clubs, organizations, rocket GUIs - you name it.

services.title: Design
services.description: I like to think my designs are playful yet minimalistic. Whether I'm designing websites, Instagram posts, or club merch, my focus is always to keep it simple.

services.title: Webmaster-ing
services.description: I have a few sites right now that I have to regularly manage updates. It's quite a long-term commitment but it's taught me a thing or two about self-regulation.

services.title: Teamwork
services.description: I truly believe that teamwork makes the dreamwork. Having worked with so many people, I know not only how to be a good team leader, but also a good team member

aboutpara: Developing websites, staying awake at hackathons, performing at retirement homes, launching rockets, organizing school events, singing at coffeehouses, and designing things - wherever, and whenever.
